"Why scheduled operations fall through — too few sign-ups, doctrine gaps, or "
"organiser calls."
msgstr ""
"Warum geplante Operationen platzen — zu wenige Anmeldungen, Doctrine-Lücken "
"oder Entscheidungen des Organisators."

